<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>التّاء والنُّون<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(و. ا. ي)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">تين:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">التِّيْنُ:</span> من الفَوَاكِهِ، الواحِدَةُ تِيْنَةٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والتِّيْنَةُ:</span> الدُّبُرُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">يتن:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">اليَتْنُ:</span> الوِلادُ المَنْكُوْسُ؛ فالوَلَدُ مُوْتَنٌ، وأَيْتَنَتِ المَرْأَةُ تُوْتِنُ إيْتَاناً.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وتن:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">الوَتِيْنُ:</span> عِرْقٌ يَسْقِي الكَبِدَ، وثَلاثَةُ أَوْتِنَةٍ، والجَميعُ الوُتُنُ.<span class="c5"> ورَجُلٌ مَوْتُوْنٌ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>إذا انْقَطَعَ وَتِيْنُهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">واسْتَوْتَنْتَ عَنّي الخَبَرَ:</span> حَبَسْتَه عَنّي.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">ووَاتَنَهُ مُوَاتَنَةً:</span> أي لَزِمَه. وهي المُقَارَبَةُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> أيضاً.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">والْوَاتِنُ من المِيَاهِ:</span> الدّائِمُ العَفِنُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">ووَتَنَ بالمَكَانِ:</span> أقَامَ به؛ وُتُوْناً.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">ووَاتَنْتُهُ مُوَاتَنَةً:</span> إذا فَعَلْتَ مِثْلَ فِعْلِه.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">والْوَتْنُ:</span> لُغَةٌ في اليَتْنِ، وقد أَوْتَنَتِ المَرْأَةُ وأَيْتَنَتْ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في الأساس: المقارنة (بالنُّون).</p> </div>